mis_exp:
# 錯誤：忘記 self 參數
class Dog:
    def bark():
        print('汪汪！')

my_dog = Dog()
my_dog.bark()  # TypeError：缺少 self 參數

# 錯誤：未呼叫建構子所需參數
class Student:
    def __init__(self, name):
        self.name = name

s = Student()  # TypeError：缺少參數 name

# 錯誤：屬性名稱拼錯
class Cat:
    def __init__(self, name):
        self.name = name

c = Cat('Mimi')
print(c.nmae)  # AttributeError：屬性名稱錯誤

practice.question:
下列程式輸出結果為何？

class Dog:
    def __init__(self, name):
        self.name = name

    def bark(self):
        print(self.name, '汪汪叫！')

my_dog = Dog('Lucky')
my_dog.bark()

下列程式哪裡錯誤？

class Car:
    def __init__(self, brand):
        self.brand = brand

my_car = Car()
print(my_car.brand)
